quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  55,68,un mein meway aur khjorin aur aanar hain
  55,69,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,70,un mein naik seerat ( aur ) khobsorat aurtain hain
  55,71,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,72,( woh ) hooren ( hain jo ) khaimon mein Mastoor ( hain )
  55,73,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,74,un ko ahal jannat se pehlay nah kisi ensaan ne haath lagaya aur nah kisi jin ne
  55,75,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,76,sabz qalinon aur nafees masnadon par takiya lagaye baithy hon ge
  55,77,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,78,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tumhara perwar-digaar jo sahib jalal vazmt hai is ka naam bara babarkat hai
  56,1,jab waqay honay wali waqay hojaye
  56,2,is ke waqay honay mein kuch jhoot nahi
  56,3,kisi ko pust kere kisi ko buland
  56,4,jab zameen bhonchal se larazne lagey
  56,5,aur pahar toot kar rezah rezah ho jaien
  56,6,phir gubhar ho kar urnay lagen
  56,7,aur tum log teen qisam hojao
  56,8,to dahinay haath walay ( subhan allah ) dahinay haath walaykiya ( hi chain mein ) hain
  56,9,aur baen haath walay ( afsos ) baen haath walaykiya ( girftar azaab ) hain
  56,10,aur jo agay bherne walay hain ( un kakiya kehna ) woh agay hi bherne walay hain
  56,11,wohi ( khuda ke ) Maqarrab hain
  56,12,Nemat ke bahishtoon mein
  56,13,woh bohat se to aglay logon mein se hon ge
  56,14,aur thoray se pichlon mein se
  56,15,( Laal o Yaqoot waghera se ) jurey hue takhton par
  56,16,aamnay samnay takiya lagaye hue
